Metadata: Kristin Beem: Building Ships for Science (Webinar August 11, 2020)
Regional Class Research Vessels: Building Shrips for Science, by Kristin Beem. This webinar took place in Corvallis, Oregon and was recorded on August 11, 2020

Hosted by Oregon Sea Grant, this webinar features Kristin Beem, a marine science systems engineer for regional class research vessels. She helps  build ships that allow scientists to conduct research at sea. Lindsay Carroll, who coordinates Oregon Sea Grant's marine education program serves as a moderator on this webinar, which was recorded on Aug. 11, 2020.
